elements.name: Interact with text box and check box

steps.name: The user is on the home page
The user clicks on the Elements option
The user selects the TextBox option
The user fills in the fields with name "Karina Gerdez", email "kagerhe@gmail.com", address "avenida 40 Bello", and secondary address "Avenida 50 Medellín"
The user clicks on the Submit button
The form should display the entered data below in the output
The user selects the CheckBox option
The user selects Check Box Home
The user selects Check Box Desktop
The user selects Check Box Notes
The user selects Check Box Documents
The user selects Check Box Workspace
The user selects Check Box Office
The user selects Check Box Download
The user selects Check Box Word
The output should display the selected checkboxes
The user selects the Radio Button option
The user selects the Yes radio button
The output should display "Yes"
The user selects the Impressive radio button
The output should display "Impressive"
The user selects the Web Table option
The user clicks on the "Add" button
The user fills the web table form with first name "Marcela", last name "Juarez", age "30", email "marcej@gmail.com", salary "5000000", and department "Operaciones"
The user submits the web table form
